'''托马斯·霍利·“汤米”·图伯维尔'''（{{lang-en|Thomas Hawley "Tommy" Tuberville}}，{{IPAc-en|ˈ|t|ʌ|b|ər|v|ɪ|l}} {{Respell|TUBB|ər|vill}}；<ref>{{Cite web|title='We need a different voice:' Tommy Tuberville says it's time to send real people to Washington D.C.|url=https://www.cbs42.com/news/politics/your-local-election-hq/we-need-a-different-voice-tommy-tuberville-says-its-time-to-send-real-people-to-washington-d-c/|date=2020-03-04|website=CBS 42|language=en-US|access-date=2020-05-16|archive-date=2021-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121012812/https://www.cbs42.com/news/politics/your-local-election-hq/we-need-a-different-voice-tommy-tuberville-says-its-time-to-send-real-people-to-washington-d-c/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，{{bd|1954年|9月18日||}}）是美国退役大学[[美式橄榄球|美式橄榄球]]教练，前球员，政治家。自2021年起担任代表[[阿拉巴马州|阿拉巴马州]]的[[美国参议院|联邦参议员]]。在进入政界之前，图伯维尔在1999年至2008年担任[[奥本大学|奥本大学]]的橄榄球主教练，并崭露头角。他还在[[密西西比大学|密西西比大学]]（1995年至1998年）、[[德克萨斯理工大学|德克萨斯理工大学]]（2010年至2012年）、[[辛辛那提大学|辛辛那提大学]]（2013年至2016年）担任过美式橄榄球主教练。

以[[共和黨_(美國)|共和黨]]人身份参加2020年阿拉巴马州联邦参议员选举，图伯维尔赢得提名，并在大选中击败民主党时任参议员[[道格·琼斯_(政治人物)|道格·琼斯]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Tommy Tuberville running for U.S. Senate|url=https://www.al.com/news/2019/04/report-tommy-tuberville-to-run-for-us-senate.html|date=2019-04-06|website=al|language=en|access-date=2020-05-16|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308001102/https://www.al.com/news/2019/04/report-tommy-tuberville-to-run-for-us-senate.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Tommy Tuberville wins the Alabama GOP Senate primary, defeating Jeff Sessions |url=https://www.vox.com/2020/7/14/21324520/tuberville-wins-gop-senate-primary-july-sessions |access-date=2020-07-14 |publisher=VOX |date=2020-07-14 |archive-date=2021-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210305215208/https://www.vox.com/2020/7/14/21324520/tuberville-wins-gop-senate-primary-july-sessions |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite news|title=Alabama U.S. Senate Election Results|language=en-US|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2020/11/03/us/elections/results-alabama-senate.html|access-date=2020-11-04|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2021-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210307232123/https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2020/11/03/us/elections/results-alabama-senate.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。上任后不久，他加入了一群共和党参议员的行列，试图推翻民主党当选总统[[喬·拜登|拜登]]在[[2020年美國總統選舉|2020年总统选举]]中战胜现任共和党总统[[唐纳德·特朗普|唐纳德·特朗普]]的选举结果。图伯维尔是反对将亚利桑那州的选举人票计算给拜登的6名共和党参议员之一，也是反对在国会选举认证期间将宾夕法尼亚州的选举人票计算给拜登的7名参议员之一；这两次反对都被参议院的其他议员否决了<ref>"Roll Call Vote 117th Congress - 1st Session". USSen. U.S. Senate. January 7, 2021. Retrieved January 7, 2021.</ref><ref>{{Cite news|last1=Wagner|first1=John|last2=Helderman|first2=Rosalind S.|title=Hawley's plan to contest electoral college vote certification ensures drawn-out process|language=en-US|work=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/congress-election-vote-certification-objection/2020/12/30/4dce936c-4ab6-11eb-839a-cf4ba7b7c48c_story.html|access-date=2021-01-08|issn=0190-8286|archive-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115071304/https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/congress-election-vote-certification-objection/2020/12/30/4dce936c-4ab6-11eb-839a-cf4ba7b7c48c_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

